description:
This is a 30 minute workout called '30 Min Elliptical Machine Low Impact Workout | Fitscope Studio' from the channel Fitscope.
The workout falls under Cardio/Elliptical and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: 30 Min Elliptical Machine Low Impact Workout | Fitscope Studio

In this low impact, intermediate level elliptical machine workout, Julia guides you through a series of  jogs, sprints & runs with modest inclines, punctuated with 2 min active recoveries.  This is both a low impact and HIIT workout. 
Soundtrack is indie rock & electronic. Great substitute for iFit workouts!
